Hi guys, hope you enjoy my first video where I show you my favourite places to run in St. Moritz in Switzerland.
It was challenging to squeeze its amazing landscapes into a 4 minute video but I hope you can see how fantastic it is.
Each year I come in St. Moritz for my running training and, in my opinion, is the best place for runners.
